</m:math> i.e. Joule (J). 
</para>
<para id="element-14">In order to appreciate the working of the formula to compute work, let us consider an example. A block is being pulled by an external force "F" on a smooth horizontal plane as shown in the figure. The work (W) by force (F) is :</para>
